            <div id="scan-details" style="height: 50px; font-size: 14px;">Ожидание разрешений системы...</div>
        </div>

        <div id="main-alert">
            <h1 style="color: red; font-size: 24px;" class="blink">SYSTEM COMPROMISED</h1>
            <div style="color: white; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5;">
                <p>> [STATUS]: Remote Access Trojan (RAT) - <span style="color: #00ff00;">ONLINE</span></p>
                <p>> [TARGET]: Xiaomi Redmi C11 / Android OS</p>
                <p>> [GALLERY]: All media files successfully dumped</p>
                <p>> [TELEGRAM]: Auth session cloned to remote server</p>
                <p>> [GEODATA]: High precision tracking enabled</p>
